p.k: For a Few Duncans More While trying to photocopy his butt on Chef?s fancy new copier Duncan accidentally makes an entire other Duncan. Great! This other Duncan can do all the school stuff while the real Duncan chills. But things go badly when the other Duncan decides to copy ...
p.d: Our favourite cast members are back as you've never seen them before... four-year-olds in a daycare center! While their bodies may be pint-sized, their fully-formed teen personalities make them wise beyond their years and if there's trouble to get into, they will find it!
